    "Released in Nov 2022, use of ChatGPT has experienced one of the fastest adoptions and its use is still increasing (Stringer & Wiggers, 2023).",
    "In fact, the release of ChatGPT has led to a wave of similar tools (e.g., Anthropic's Claude, Google Bard, and Meta's Llama).",
